 "remarks": "Experience turnkey living in this beautifully appointed three-bedroom townhouse, ideally located within easy walking distance of town, restaurants, boutiques, and local amenities. Thoughtfully designed with an open-concept layout, the inviting main level is perfect for entertaining or relaxing by the fireplace and features 9-foot ceilings throughout. The gourmet kitchen is equipped with Viking appliances, quartz countertops, and flows seamlessly into the living and dining areas. A private office or den with built-in cabinetry offers the perfect work-from-home space, while French doors open to a charming fenced patio and garden for indoor-outdoor living. The upper level includes a spacious primary suite with vaulted ceilings, a walk-in closet, and a luxurious spa bath, along with two additional bedrooms and a dedicated laundry room. The finished lower level expands the home&apos;s versatility with an ideal playroom or recreation space and a newly added full bathroom, making this exceptional townhouse as functional as it is elegant. This unit&apos;s HOA Association fee is calculated by the owner based on his estimated monthly cost for the front unit. The total HOA Association fee is shared just between the two units. Please ask listing agent for further information.",
